FOR NEW DOWNLOADERS:

It seems as if Tuneup HQ issued a kill switch in one of their updates. First thing to do when you get THIS torrent is kill the auto-updates from Settings>General>Updates> AND UNCHECK "Check automatically for updates". This prevents any locking out of the program from an update. By the way, why would this type of program need an update anyway? Bottom line is, it does what it does beautifully, needs nothing extra, so turn off updates.

Don't Q_Q about trojans, its a false positive. Don't Q_Q about error message I stated above, rerun this program and install again then turn off updates to not make it happen. Don't Q_Q about speeds/peers/99% downloaded, the speed is fine. And please +1 this torrent!
